{"type": "article", "id": 24735, "title": "“盒子”沙发", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-31T06:52:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110324YkIis45uo3vzLKWb.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是比利时设计师 Alain Gilles 为意大利家居品牌 Bonaldo 设计的沙发，他认为沙发是从一个纸盒子里变化出来的，经过切割调整，再安装上金属结构。这组沙发就有着方正的轮廓，下面的腿非常纤细，通过体量的对比突出沙发本身的宽大，也能让人感受到舒适，<a href=\"http://www.alaingilles.com/en/project/52/structure-sofa\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110321ba5hLx83HuR4gliJ.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.42666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110322sPHIAB0ghCTpoi6U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021103226oTSpvCmqBsa1nJb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110323aenk3sY1OJUrwC9o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110323mrF5M3GP0ADiQdbK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}